{"tid":1031734,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"求救，有小學老師煽動校園欺凌！ (2)","createTime":"2019-02-22T00:26:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-22T08:27:11.000Z","uid":48234,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"d46377cc1a9da48e3b87dc925e4126431a27b850","tid":1031734,"uid":48234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T00:26:48.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">原post已爆，幫佢再開，以下為原文</span></span><br />\n<br />\n事源係我上年開始幫一個小五男仔補習 <br />\n本身淨係知佢係培正小學讀咗4年，今年先轉校 <br />\n佢平時都幾活潑同百厭，但每次提起培正/見到培正啲工作紙，佢就會好驚同好大脾氣 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最近佢父母同我講番件事，我先知佢以前比同學打，點知班教畜無停止欺凌不得止，仲因為想佢收口而叫埋其他人一齊加入bully，逼到佢兩個月內轉校&hellip;. <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n打番件事出黎，係想更多人知道班教畜做嘅好事，佢地愈驚件事揚出去就愈要全世界睇清呢間小學！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同埋，想各位巴絲比吓意見，點樣做先逼到校方出黎比個交代<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我就咁聽完都睇唔過眼!<br />\n<br />\n<strong> 事情經過</strong><br />\n <span style=\"color: red;\">語言欺凌:</span> 2017新學年，受害人(下稱X) 收到班上男仔(下稱李)匿名寫比佢嘅字條，內容包括恐嚇X，預言X嘅父母會死。類似字條一共有5張，已經令到X日日好唔安落。 X比咗字條班主任(劉)睇，但劉話只係一般紙仔完全唔處理，仲沒收咗部份字條。 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">身體欺凌:</span> 11月李開始打X背部。X同劉講，劉依然話唔想處理，話件事交比訓導(下稱黃)算。 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一個星期後李小息時又打X，X不適到當晚就要父母帶佢睇醫生(所以有醫生紙證明呢件事)。父母同黃講，黃稱上星期嘅打人事件因為已經一個星期，所以file closed <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，話會調查吓今次。<br />\n 打人嘅時候X有朋友見到，後尾訓導洗腦個朋友話無呢件事發生過，黃之後便聲稱調查後搵唔到目擊證人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n X 父母一路有搵證據比黃，但黃話全部唔成立。後尾黃聲稱打人事件證據不足，所以又可以close file <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> (真係龍門任佢擺)<br />\nX父母搵培正社工講，社工淨係話自己就黎退休，唔想搞咁多野就無處理到。 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">兩件打人事件close file之後，黃就帶頭欺凌X。</span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n 1.黃去X班房叫大家遠離X，X一時之間無哂朋友，精神嚴重崩潰 <br />\n2.黃係小息時段, 搵兩個低年級同學跟著X去廁所,X形容好似係黑社會一樣, 非常恐怖. 身心受到極大傷害(X亦因此嚇到唔敢去廁所) <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n3.黃屈X寫影響校風紙條並傳開去, (X表示沒有寫這紙仔, 更不是他的字跡, 要討回公道) <br />\n4.黃恐嚇X如果再講大話訧要叫註校警宫王警長處分X<br />\n<br />\n真心想知，點解成間學校無一個人做到野? 本身打人事件老師好好處理就無野，但老師個個推卸責任，仲帶頭玩9學生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n培正小學真心cls<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />希望大家幫幫手推post，等所有人見到呢間小學有幾醜惡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d74a03c9d034093e6f60e61ad6ee242945a2f90","tid":1031734,"uid":48234,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T00:27:21.000Z","msg":"黃敬儒全家百病纏身，行動不能，全身劇痛，長命百歲，就算有安樂死都唔批佢哋<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://lih.kg/cnjBzS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://lih.kg/cnjBzS</a>"},{"pid":"143350f0a1c75522aa59ddd32915381c29f03a13","tid":1031734,"uid":226231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T00:31:59.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b0f52aef495439ed3794fba5349d32f09bcee31","tid":1031734,"uid":21423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T00:32:39.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"aaddbd045259bf317d39a02431110ed6874a8d14","tid":1031734,"uid":236368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T01:02:18.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d81f923551c7dc910f89d030ab3853e5d210fca3","tid":1031734,"uid":236368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T03:25:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67022fb550198a627bb7d97370c2e566c0296586","tid":1031734,"uid":48234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T03:25:57.000Z","msg":"屌佢老母蝗敬儒"},{"pid":"a028f3d5c6ef99a30ee8f85991ae3da54b2114ff","tid":1031734,"uid":48234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T03:26:43.000Z","msg":"口講道義嘅黑社會點解唔去打鳩蝗敬儒一鑊?<br />\n<a href=\"http://lih.kg/cnkkHS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://lih.kg/cnkkHS</a>"},{"pid":"e2f6a388d43e867d1bc8bf1c35f095bc398b7380","tid":1031734,"uid":48234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T05:17:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0be67e1f3064591bf0061ef2b27074d75d351f0","tid":1031734,"uid":48234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T08:27:11.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">多行不義必自斃</span></span>"}]}